http://www.oxo.com/p-363-cake-tester.aspx

The OXO Good Grips Cake Tester is the perfect tool for gauging when cakes are ready to come out of the oven. Insert the stainless steel wire into the center of your cake; if it comes out clean, the cake is ready. No more wasting toothpicks or wooden matches for this simple task. A soft grip is comfortable to hold, and the Cake Tester is dishwasher safe.

transcripts: Nothing says happy birthday like a homemade birthday cake our cake tester will help your cakes turn out perfectly year after year the oxo cake tester is the perfect tool for gauging when cakes are ready to come out of the oven. Simply insert the stainless steel wire into the center of your cake when it comes out clean your cake is ready. No more wasting toothpicks or wooden matches for the simple task. The soft grip it's comfortable hold and it has a hanging hole for convenient storage. The cake fester is also dishwasher safe. Here's a good tip one oxonian uses her cake tester to hit the pesky reset button on her wireless router.
